    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic repairs. The engine currently runs roughly, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, suggesting an overhaul may be necessary soon. Externally, the paint is faded with several deep scratches and minor rust spots, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
      "price": 7500.0,
