    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, boasting supple, premium leather and high-gloss accents that look as if they just left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history and a whisper-quiet engine. From the untouched alloy wheels to the crystal-clear headlights, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is a collector-grade opportunity for the most discerning buyer who demands a vehicle that looks and drives like it belongs on a pedestal.",
      "price": 48500.0,
